cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.GR 

This paper deals with object detection in aerial images, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves using periodic vectors to represent the orientation of objects, which is a technique that falls under machine learning (cs.AI) and statistical learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses a novel IoU calculation method for long objects, which is related to robotics (cs.RO) and graphics (cs.GR).
